## Quick reference

| Operation | Pattern | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- |
| List my projects (page render) | RSC + Server Loader | `getCurrentUser()` + `redirect()` + domain loader (e.g. `listProductsWithMediaForSsr`) |
| List my projects (client polling) | Route Handler → Server Loader | Wrap loader in `ok({ ... })` |
| Update my profile | Route Handler → Server Handler | Validate, transact, return DTO |
| Generate image / video | Route Handler → Server Handler → Queue | Reserve credits, enqueue, return task id |
| AI chat streaming | Route Handler with `streamText` | Use AI Gateway model strings |
| Stripe webhook | `/api/webhooks/stripe/route.ts` | Verify signature, dispatch handler |
| Fal callback | `/api/webhooks/fal/<event>/route.ts` | Token-verify, write status, publish SSE |
| Free monthly credits grant | `/api/cron/grant-free-monthly-credits/route.ts` | Vercel Cron schedule in `vercel.ts` |
| Persist media to R2 (async) | `/api/queues/persist-media-to-r2/route.ts` | Queue worker, idempotent |
| Realtime task progress | `/api/realtime/<feature>/[id]/route.ts` | SSE + Redis pub/sub |
| Admin / cross-user query | Server Handler called from a guarded Route Handler | Explicit `requireAdmin` check |

